{"tid":2437363,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拜登簽署行政命令指示聯邦機構採取措施促進投票權","createTime":"2021-03-07T23:29:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T23:40:39.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1e3df496eb9755600b8737286060da9c8da0cf8a","tid":2437363,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:29:03.000Z","msg":"拜登簽署行政命令指示聯邦機構採取措施促進投票權<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579289-20210308.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579289-20210308.htm&d=7kduTEFmP9pIRK3EkT058mINpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=665b53b9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1579289-20210308.htm&h=2cb20de4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1579289-20210308.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n美國總統拜登趁阿拉巴馬州「血腥星期天」56周年紀念，簽署行政命令，指示聯邦機構在200天內採取措施促進投票權。<br />\n<br />\n拜登在預先錄製的講話中表示，每個合資格的選民都應該能夠投票並被重視。<br />\n<br />\n行政命令包括指示聯邦機構擴大選民登記和選舉資訊的存取權限；呼籲各機構負責人提出計劃，讓聯邦僱員有時間投票或擔任無黨派的票站義工；並推動對政府投票網站的全面改革。<br />\n<br />\n1965年大約有600名民權人士在阿拉巴馬州塞爾瑪遊行爭取投票權時，被警員毆打。事件成為當年《投票權法》獲得通過的轉捩點。"},{"pid":"bd55dde5e0322fad3c33d2ddf2fb21bbacdb5867","tid":2437363,"uid":95577,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:32:10.000Z","msg":"條友好似淨係識簽行政命令<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0e0f8e3d66dc87ef0408286cf3b2e70817865e4","tid":2437363,"uid":226156,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:34:27.000Z","msg":"爭取仙人投票權<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc1e4e2ff2e84fca5f560dc4464b4dd719474c1a","tid":2437363,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:34:50.000Z","msg":"造票合法化<br />\n民主黨一黨專政<br />\n千秋萬世<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add3e2de3bcd374ae351e9252a90bf2fb854e189","tid":2437363,"uid":130385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-07T23:40:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />想網上投票"}]}